sub_title: individual speech coach in English (online) and freelance journalist
summary:
* journalistic generalist with a couple of specialities:
* individual speech coach in English for keynote speakers. Please watch  https://youtu.be/_cpw0FZwpXw 
PROVEN EXPERTISE IN:
- maritime and logistic affairs
- architecture
- industrial design
- human interest
I've got some experience as a radio presenter and media consultant.

Specialities: Teaching fluency in English (also online), acting as co-host at conferences, hosting radio programs, maritime affairs.  Generalist. I'm acting as a PR consultant if need be, and also as a kind of Ombudsman and campaigner for good causes.
